info.description:
Beautiful Detail
This is a striking and elegant sofa. Buttoning adds texture and shape, while scrolled arms bring just the right amount of opulence.

Genuine Comfort
Large and deep seated, with foam cushioning giving a medium-soft sit. In soft fabric with dark stain legs - scatter cushions included.
